import React from 'react'
import Row from 'react-bootstrap/esm/Row'
import Col from 'react-bootstrap/esm/Col'
function View() {
  return (
    <>
    <Row>
        <Col sm={12} md={6} lg={4} xl={3}>
            
        </Col>
        
    </Row>
    </>
  )
}

export default View
